    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360410/extras/26c3cb67d71154844d2b5e757116d2c5.poster.avif?t=1747864302\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360410/extras/26c3cb67d71154844d2b5e757116d2c5.webm?t=1747864302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360410/extras/26c3cb67d71154844d2b5e757116d2c5.mp4?t=1747864302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好在Domenation中体验肾上腺素飙升的挑战，每一秒都至关重要！待在圆顶内以最大化你的时间，智胜对手。通过独特的皮肤和武器风格自定义角色，确保即使在失败中也能留下印记。此外，不要忘记你的Frens，你的忠实伙伴，他们与您一起进化，为您在生存战斗中提供重要支持。你会是最后一个站着的玩家吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360410/extras/d0feaf5581df5f7c8e11a8fc08c2f039.poster.avif?t=1747864302\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360410/extras/d0feaf5581df5f7c8e11a8fc08c2f039.webm?t=1747864302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360410/extras/d0feaf5581df5f7c8e11a8fc08c2f039.mp4?t=1747864302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在Deathclock模式中，你只剩下5分钟。时间一到，游戏结束 – 你就出局了。别以为你可以轻松应对；在淘气的圆顶外，时间流逝得更快。留在里面，保持警惕，否则就告别吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360410/extras/e7406a8ab48da677c9943358ad1776f9.poster.avif?t=1747864302\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360410/extras/e7406a8ab48da677c9943358ad1776f9.webm?t=1747864302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360410/extras/e7406a8ab48da677c9943358ad1776f9.mp4?t=1747864302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >生存并非有保障。掌控圆顶，明智地利用每一秒，击败对手。最后剩下时间的玩家就是胜利者。你有能力坚持到最后吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360410/extras/2797c895f5fab234435f5fa756357373.poster.avif?t=1747864302\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360410/extras/2797c895f5fab234435f5fa756357373.webm?t=1747864302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360410/extras/2797c895f5fab234435f5fa756357373.mp4?t=1747864302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为什么平淡地离开？选择各种角色皮肤、武器样式和头像。如果你要离开，那就潇洒一点！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360410/extras/d334bccccf8cff63ad821579369f04ef.poster.avif?t=1747864302\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360410/extras/d334bccccf8cff63ad821579369f04ef.webm?t=1747864302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360410/extras/d334bccccf8cff63ad821579369f04ef.mp4?t=1747864302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每场比赛都是提高排名的机会。生存、超越并智取对手，证明你是最好的。即使你被淘汰，你也会被记住——至少在其他人取代你的位置之前！</p>",
